txt.en: 'Intruders? You will make a wonderful gift to Goeolgon!'
'Your rabble has already failed the Mistress once...'
'Fail her again, and it will be your hide!'
'What is Goeolgon doing in the tower?'
The ring Narchuil is being studied by the Enemy in Barad Dúrgul.
'Goeolgon is defying his orders...don't make things worse by letting your guard down.'
'Amarthiel will have Goeolgon on a pike when she learns that he has not gone North.'
You have found Narucham, and it appears that he has been dead for some time now.  You should give him a proper burial and then return to Gwathryn.
Enter Barad Dúrgul and recover the ring Narchuil.
'My Mistress will be pleased when I bring her thine heads.'
'And after I have dealt with thee, I will not be troubled in the search that remains.'
'Come, come! Thou canst join the craven fool who dared trespass upon Barad Dúrgul.'
